.TH "LIGHTNING-CHANNEL-REBALANCE-CHECK" 1 "May 2026" "lightning 0.6.0" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
lightning-channel-rebalance-check \- list channels that need rebalancing
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B lightning channel-rebalance-check
.RB [ --threshold
.IR ratio ]
.SH DESCRIPTION
Returns channels whose balance ratio is outside the acceptable range
(default threshold: 0.3).
.PP
Output:
.nf
[{channel_id, peer_id, balance_ratio, local_msat, total_msat, direction}]
.fi
.SH EXIT STATUS
.TP
.B 0
Always.
.SH SEE ALSO
.BR lightning-rebalance (1),
.BR lightning-channel-balance-ratio (1)
